result.name: wiltshire-council-spending-over-five-hundred
result.notes:
This dataset contains details of payments made by Wiltshire Council to suppliers.  Data published monthly.

NB: publication threshold of individual transactions exceeding £500 was reduced in August 2012 to transactions equal to £250 or over.

odi-certificate.title: Wiltshire Council - Payments over £500 to suppliers
